msgstr "open"

#: ../../O/open.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../O/open.rst:9
msgid ""
"Abbreviation for ‘open (or left) parenthesis’ — used when necessary to "
"eliminate oral ambiguity. To read aloud the LISP form (DEFUN FOO (X) (PLUS X"
" 1)) one might say: \"Open defun foo, open eks close, open, plus eks one, "
"close close.\""
msgstr ""
"‘開き(または左)括弧’の略——口頭での曖昧さを排除する必要があるときに使われる。LISPの式(DEFUN FOO (X) (PLUS X "
"1))を声に出して読むには、こう言うかもしれない。「Open defun foo, open eks close, open, plus eks "
"one, close close.」"
